and claims, is Hans-Georg Gadamer who also demonstrates the compatibility of the Platonic dialogues with the directions of continental thinking.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aPhilosophy, Europeanx20th century. 0aPhilosophy, Europeany20th century. 0aPhilosophy, Moderny20th century. 4aPhilosophy : Ancient Greek Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : History of Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Plato. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / Phenomenology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791484555423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791484555/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles